						               													<description>After the destruction of his TerraLunar Impulsion Beam at the hands of his nemesis Legacy, Baron Blade narrowly made his escape from the Freedom Five. Now, he has returned, but without the devices and minions he usually employs to distract the heroes. This time, the Baron has hidden bombs throughout the city of Megalopolis and is threatening to blow the entire city sky high if the heroes do not disarm the bombs in time. However, he has sent video footage of his bombs to the Freedom Five headquarters, giving them the clues they need to find and dispose of the explosives. What maniacal plan does this madman have up his sleeves, and when he reveals them, will the heroes be able to save the city, or will they be caught in Baron Blade's twisted trap?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Vengeful Baron Blade is a promo card that was given as part of the Kickstarter project for Sentinels of the Multiverse 2nd Edition &amp;amp; Infernal Relics expansion. The oversized version is available as part of the Sentinels of the Multiverse: Villain Oversized Cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
